{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"BIPV Structural Load API","description":"\n## BIPV Structural Load API\nStructural design loads for building-integrated photovoltaic (BIPV)\nfacade and roof systems. Developed by a structural engineering researcher\nspecialising in BIPV.\nSend building geometry, panel specification, and installation details —\nget back wind pressures, dead loads, ULS load combinations, bracket\ndesign forces, and serviceability deflection checks. All outputs are\nfully cited to the source standard or publication.\n---\n### What It Calculates\n| Output | Standard |\n|---|---|\n| Peak wind velocity pressure qp(z) | EN 1991-1-4:2005 Eq.(4.8) |\n| External pressure coefficients Cpe | EN 1991-1-4:2005 Table 7.1 |\n| Air permeability correction factor | Miller & Kopp (2024) DOI:10.3389/fbuil.2024.1398472 |\n| Net wind pressure on panel (Pa, kN/m²) | EN 1991-1-4:2005 §5.2 |\n| Panel + mounting dead load | EN 1991-1-1:2002 Annex A |\n| ULS load combinations | EN 1990:2002 Table A1.2(B) |\n| Bracket shear and pull-out forces (kN) | EN 1990:2002 §6.4 |\n| SLS deflection check (L/200) | Yin et al. (2023) Eng. Structures 285:116021 |\n| US wind loads (C&C) | ASCE 7-22 Chapter 30 |\n---\n### Scope\n**Covered:** Wind loads · Dead loads · ULS/SLS combinations ·\nBracket design forces · Ventilated facade air permeability correction ·\nEN (Eurocode) and ASCE 7-22 (US) standards.\n**Not covered:** Glass stress design (EN 16612:2019) ·\nSeismic loads (EN 1998-1) · Connection capacity (EN 1993-1-8).\n---\n### Authentication\n`X-API-Key` header required.\n**Free** — 10 calls · **Pro** $49/mo — 2,000 calls + all-zones endpoint\n","version":"1.0.0"},"paths":{"/":{"get":{"tags":["Info"],"summary":"Root","operationId":"root__get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/health":{"get":{"tags":["Info"],"summary":"Health","operationId":"health_health_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/calculate":{"post":{"tags":["Calculation"],"summary":"Calculate Loads","description":"Full BIPV Structural Load Calculation — EN 1991-1-4 + ASCE 7-22.","operationId":"calculate_loads_calculate_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/FullCalculationRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}},"security":[{"APIKeyHeader":[]}]}},"/all-zones":{"post":{"tags":["Calculation"],"summary":"Calculate All Zones","description":"All EN 1991-1-4 facade zones in one call. Pro/Enterprise only.","operationId":"calculate_all_zones_all_zones_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/FullCalculationRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}},"security":[{"APIKeyHeader":[]}]}},"/reference/terrain-categories":{"get":{"tags":["Reference"],"summary":"Terrain Categories","operationId":"terrain_categories_reference_terrain_categories_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/reference/panel-weights":{"get":{"tags":["Reference"],"summary":"Panel Weights","operationId":"panel_weights_reference_panel_weights_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/reference/pressure-zones":{"get":{"tags":["Reference"],"summary":"Pressure Zones","operationId":"pressure_zones_reference_pressure_zones_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/reference/wind-speed-map":{"get":{"tags":["Reference"],"summary":"Wind Speed Guide","operationId":"wind_speed_guide_reference_wind_speed_map_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/pricing":{"get":{"tags":["Info"],"summary":"Pricing","operationId":"pricing_pricing_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}}},"components":{"schemas":{"FullCalculationRequest":{"properties":{"site":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SiteInput"},"panel":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/PanelInput"},"installation":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/InstallationInput"}},"type":"object","required":["site","panel","installation"],"title":"FullCalculationRequest","example":{"installation":{"air_gap_mm":50,"bracket_spacing_m":0.85,"cpi":0.0,"facade_zone":"B","fixing_points":4,"installation_type":"ventilated_facade_bracket","is_ventilated":true,"surface_type":"wall","tilt_deg":90},"panel":{"panel_height_m":1.7,"panel_thickness_mm":12.0,"panel_type":"glass_glass_standard","panel_width_m":1.0},"site":{"altitude_m":50,"basic_wind_speed_ms":28,"building_depth_m":20,"building_height_m":30,"building_width_m":40,"standard":"EN","terrain_category":"II"}}},"HTTPValidationError":{"properties":{"detail":{"items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ValidationError"},"type":"array","title":"Detail"}},"type":"object","title":"HTTPValidationError"},"InstallationInput":{"properties":{"installation_type":{"type":"string","title":"Installation Type","default":"ventilated_facade_bracket"},"facade_zone":{"type":"string","title":"Facade Zone","default":"B"},"tilt_deg":{"type":"number","maximum":90.0,"minimum":0.0,"title":"Tilt Deg","default":90.0},"is_ventilated":{"type":"boolean","title":"Is Ventilated","default":true},"air_gap_mm":{"type":"number","maximum":500.0,"minimum":0.0,"title":"Air Gap Mm","default":50.0},"fixing_points":{"type":"integer","maximum":12.0,"minimum":